You are here: Unified Analytics Experiences

With unified experiences in Analytics tab, mobile, and Slack, you can interact with all of your Lightning reports and dashboards, CRM Analytics assets, Tableau views, and Einstein Discovery models and predictions.

Available in: Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs) and Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Group (View Only), Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Unified experiences bring all of your Salesforce Analytics together for easy access, personalization, and collaboration with your teams.
